      ],
      "records": [
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x00e0",
          "selector": 1,
          "cc_arg": 6,
          "speaker": "管家麥克",
          "text_id": 19,
          "text": "〔管家麥克〕\\n$n，很對不起，公爵有令，不讓您進家門．"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x00e9",
          "selector": 2,
          "cc_arg": 0,
          "speaker": null,
          "text_id": 20,
          "text": "知道了，我只是想跟你告別呀．"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x00f2",
          "selector": 1,
          "cc_arg": 6,
          "speaker": "管家麥克",
          "text_id": 21,
          "text": "大海像瞬間即改變其表情的怪物一樣危險．$n先生，請您一定要多加小心啊．"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0.run4",
      "title": "$s公爵",
      "start": 258,
      "start_hex": "0x0102",
      "end": 510,
      "end_hex": "0x01fe",
      "record_count": 28,
      "text_range": [
        22,
        49
      ],
      "selectors": {
        "1": 17,
        "2": 11
      },
      "cc_args": [
        18,
        0
      ],
      "speakers": [
        "$s公爵"
      ],
      "records": [
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x0102",
          "selector": 2,
          "cc_arg": 0,
          "speaker": null,
          "text_id": 22,
          "text": "聽說父親叫我．"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x010b",
          "selector": 1,
          "cc_arg": 18,
          "speaker": "$s公爵",
          "text_id": 23,
          "text": "〔$s公爵〕\\n噢，是$n啊，你現在劍術練得如何了？"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x0114",
          "selector": 2,
          "cc_arg": 0,
          "speaker": null,
          "text_id": 24,
          "text": "還行，當然只是跟以前比較說的，若和父親比試的話，只能五場贏一場吧．"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x011d",
          "selector": 1,
          "cc_arg": 18,
          "speaker": "$s公爵",
          "text_id": 25,
          "text": "是嗎，那麼航海術呢，學好啦？"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x0126",
          "selector": 2,
          "cc_arg": 0,
          "speaker": null,
          "text_id": 26,
          "text": "大致從理論上學了一些，但沒有實際經驗，只是紙上談兵呀！"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x012f",
          "selector": 1,
          "cc_arg": 18,
          "speaker": "$s公爵",
          "text_id": 27,
          "text": "是嗎，那麼對地理學呢，擅長嗎？"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x0138",
          "selector": 2,
          "cc_arg": 0,
          "speaker": null,
          "text_id": 28,
          "text": "這個事嗎，由於不允許我離開里斯本，只能從書本上學了一些．"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x0141",
          "selector": 1,
          "cc_arg": 18,
          "speaker": "$s公爵",
          "text_id": 29,
          "text": "$n，不要小看書本呀．書是先人的智慧，能把你從困境中救出來．"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x014a",
          "selector": 2,
          "cc_arg": 0,
          "speaker": null,
          "text_id": 30,
          "text": "是．"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x0153",
          "selector": 1,
          "cc_arg": 18,
          "speaker": "$s公爵",
          "text_id": 31,
          "text": "$n，你彈琴怎麼樣？"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x015c",
          "selector": 2,
          "cc_arg": 0,
          "speaker": null,
          "text_id": 32,
          "text": "那是個人的愛好，沒法在人家的面前彈奏．"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x0165",
          "selector": 1,
          "cc_arg": 18,
          "speaker": "$s公爵",
          "text_id": 33,
          "text": "是嗎？聽說你得到許多女孩子們的好感呀！"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x016e",
          "selector": 2,
          "cc_arg": 0,
          "speaker": null,
          "text_id": 34,
          "text": "請不要笑話我．"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x0177",
          "selector": 1,
          "cc_arg": 18,
          "speaker": "$s公爵",
          "text_id": 35,
          "text": "哈哈哈，有機會讓我聽聽吧！"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x0180",
          "selector": 1,
          "cc_arg": 18,
          "speaker": "$s公爵",
          "text_id": 36,
          "text": "$n！"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x0189",
          "selector": 2,
          "cc_arg": 0,
          "speaker": null,
          "text_id": 37,
          "text": "是．"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x0192",
          "selector": 1,
          "cc_arg": 18,
          "speaker": "$s公爵",
          "text_id": 38,
          "text": "今天有事告訴你．"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x019b",
          "selector": 2,
          "cc_arg": 0,
          "speaker": null,
          "text_id": 39,
          "text": "是什麼事啊？"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x01a4",
          "selector": 1,
          "cc_arg": 18,
          "speaker": "$s公爵",
          "text_id": 40,
          "text": "你也知道吧，當我在你那個年齡時，已率領艦隊去討伐海盜了．"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x01ad",
          "selector": 2,
          "cc_arg": 0,
          "speaker": null,
          "text_id": 41,
          "text": "是，我明白．"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x01b6",
          "selector": 1,
          "cc_arg": 18,
          "speaker": "$s公爵",
          "text_id": 42,
          "text": "過去，不允許你從這個港口出航，是因為我擔心你不成熟，容易出事．"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x01bf",
          "selector": 1,
          "cc_arg": 18,
          "speaker": "$s公爵",
          "text_id": 43,
          "text": "可是$s家族的人，不能老在陸地上待著．"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x01c8",
          "selector": 1,
          "cc_arg": 18,
          "speaker": "$s公爵",
          "text_id": 44,
          "text": "你已經俱備了一定的知識，下一步是在海上實際鍛鍊．"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x01d1",
          "selector": 1,
          "cc_arg": 18,
          "speaker": "$s公爵",
          "text_id": 45,
          "text": "這次派你去探險是葡萄牙首相兼海軍大臣萊昂·$s下達的命令．"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x01da",
          "selector": 2,
          "cc_arg": 0,
          "speaker": null,
          "text_id": 46,
          "text": "是．"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x01e3",
          "selector": 1,
          "cc_arg": 18,
          "speaker": "$s公爵",
          "text_id": 47,
          "text": "去找出叫普萊斯特·約翰的國，也許你覺得這對你過於嚴厲．但是，除非你找到普萊斯特·約翰國，不然不許回家．"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x01ec",
          "selector": 1,
          "cc_arg": 18,
          "speaker": "$s公爵",
          "text_id": 48,
          "text": "另外，我要發出公告，讓全城的人把你當作平民對待，你要有心理準備．"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x01f5",
          "selector": 1,
          "cc_arg": 18,
          "speaker": "$s公爵",
          "text_id": 49,
          "text": "你的船已叫造船廠製造，在這期間作好出航前的準備吧．"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
