          "offset_hex": "0x05fe",
          "selector": 1,
          "cc_arg": 31,
          "speaker": "老水手洛克",
          "text_id": 142,
          "text": "少爺，目前準備做什麼？"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x0607",
          "selector": 2,
          "cc_arg": 0,
          "speaker": null,
          "text_id": 143,
          "text": "想先遊覽一下各地的港口．"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x0610",
          "selector": 1,
          "cc_arg": 31,
          "speaker": "老水手洛克",
          "text_id": 144,
          "text": "這個主意不太高明．"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x0619",
          "selector": 2,
          "cc_arg": 0,
          "speaker": null,
          "text_id": 145,
          "text": "為什麼？"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x0622",
          "selector": 1,
          "cc_arg": 31,
          "speaker": "老水手洛克",
          "text_id": 146,
          "text": "海上航行要花巨大的費用，而我們沒有足夠的資金啊．"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x062b",
          "selector": 1,
          "cc_arg": 31,
          "speaker": "老水手洛克",
          "text_id": 147,
          "text": "飲水不必花錢買，這暫且不提，但招募水手，買糧食等都是不小的開銷呀．"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x0634",
          "selector": 2,
          "cc_arg": 0,
          "speaker": null,
          "text_id": 148,
          "text": "你是說這些錢不夠用吧．"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x063d",
          "selector": 1,
          "cc_arg": 31,
          "speaker": "老水手洛克",
          "text_id": 149,
          "text": "是的，勉強夠用一個月的．但到那時候再想辦法就太晚了．"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x0646",
          "selector": 1,
          "cc_arg": 31,
          "speaker": "老水手洛克",
          "text_id": 150,
          "text": "遊覽各地港口，我贊成．"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x064f",
          "selector": 1,
          "cc_arg": 32,
          "speaker": "恩里克神父",
          "text_id": 151,
          "text": "洛克先生的意思是在沿途做生意吧？"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x0658",
          "selector": 1,
          "cc_arg": 31,
          "speaker": "老水手洛克",
          "text_id": 152,
          "text": "對對對，是這個意思．"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x0661",
          "selector": 2,
          "cc_arg": 0,
          "speaker": null,
          "text_id": 153,
          "text": "如果做生意，我們做什麼買賣呢？"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x066a",
          "selector": 1,
          "cc_arg": 32,
          "speaker": "恩里克神父",
          "text_id": 154,
          "text": "要是在里斯本的話，應該買它的特產岩鹽．"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x0673",
          "selector": 2,
          "cc_arg": 0,
          "speaker": null,
          "text_id": 155,
          "text": "……"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x067c",
          "selector": 1,
          "cc_arg": 32,
          "speaker": "恩里克神父",
          "text_id": 156,
          "text": "我以前在教會當過會計，對這些比較了解．"
        },
        {
          "offset_hex": "0x0685",
          "selector": 1,
          "cc_arg": 32,
          "speaker": "恩里克神父",
          "text_id": 157,
          "text": "在這個港口花大約40枚金幣買的岩鹽，能在地中海的其它港口賣到60枚以上．"
        }
      ]
    },
